metadata.title: Densmore's Menominee Music
metadata.description: A collection of songs of the Menominee people, collected by Frances Densmore between 1925 and 1929 and published in her 1932 *Menominee  Music*. The songs were digitally encoded by Daniel Shanahan and Eva  Shanahan.

issues.title: Source preview page numbers
issues.description: The publication preview links do not always link to the exact right page.

songs.title: Song Received from the Spirit Women
A Spirit Woman Gives a Name
songs.lyrics_translation: Kakikcasin names me; the spirits

songs.title: The East God Gave Us this Dance
comments: Drum rhythm: continuous eigth-notes, accented on every other note (i.e., every quarter)
songs.lyrics_translation: The east god (sun) who moves across the sky in a day gave this dance to an Indian in a dream

songs.title: Song to the East God
songs.lyrics_translation: East god (sun), you are the greatest god

songs.title: Song in Honor of the Drum
Song for the Person to be Adopted
Dancing Song from the East God (a)
Dancing Song from the East God (b)
Dancing Song from the East God (c)
Dancing Song from the East God (d)
In Four Days
songs.lyrics_translation: I will be alive only four days

songs.title: Dancing Song from the South God (a)
Dancing Song from the South God (b)
Dancing Song from the South God (c)
comments: The parts in 2/8 and 3/8 meter have tempo quaver=184 (so quarter=92)

songs.title: Dancing Song from the South God (d)
Dancing Song from the South God (e)
Dancing Song from the South God (f)
My Gay Dress
songs.lyrics_translation: You will dance for me in my gay dress

songs.title: I Offer My Song
songs.lyrics_translation: When I begin this I offer my song, so I may succeed in getting game

songs.title: I Will Find Game
songs.lyrics_translation: I am now going to look for game and am sure that I will find it

songs.title: I Will Get a Buck
songs.lyrics_translation: I am going to get a buck and I will pack him

songs.title: I Will Shoot Him Through the Heart
songs.lyrics_translation: When I am at a buck I will shoot him through the heart

songs.title: My Tapping Stick
songs.lyrics_translation: I am now going to use my tapping stick

songs.title: You Are Struggling
songs.lyrics_translation: Tomorrow, when I am hunting, you will be struggling and I will shoot you through the heart

songs.title: The Slender-legged Animals
songs.lyrics_translation: When hunting I want to see the slender-legged animals

songs.title: Song After the Feast
songs.lyrics_translation: I bring the ewe deer

songs.title: War Bundle Dance Song (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: In the middle of the great lake I went around

songs.title: He Carries the War Bundle
songs.lyrics_translation: He walks and carries it on his back

songs.title: The War Bundle Causes a Fog
I Am Standing On a Cloud
Pigeon's Dream Song
songs.lyrics_translation: Your tribe will come to you to be cured of sickness

songs.title: Dream Song
songs.lyrics_translation: In the heavens a noise like the rustling of the trees

songs.title: Dream Song Concerning the Sun (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am the one, traveling

songs.title: Dream Song Concerning the Sun (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: I know the heavens

songs.title: Song of the Thunderers
songs.lyrics_translation: We are coming and will cover the earth

songs.title: Song Concerning the Kinewuk
songs.lyrics_translation: The voice of the kinewuk comes beforet hem announcing their approach

songs.title: Song of the Little Whirlwind
songs.lyrics_translation: The little whirlwind says, "One who whirls with the wind they call me, the spirits"

songs.title: Dream of Buffalo (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am the chief of all the animals that walk

songs.title: Dream of Buffalo (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: In the south I stand

songs.title: Song for Working Magic
songs.lyrics_translation: The pipe that I use to do this

songs.title: Juggler's Song (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am going home

songs.title: Juggler's Song (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: The inside of my house is full

songs.title: Song During Treatment of the Sick (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: My lodge stands solid. I walk all over the world

songs.title: Song During Treatment of the Sick (b)
Song of the Woodpecker
songs.lyrics_translation: Woodpecker they call me, the spirits. A person may have worms in him

songs.title: Song of the Healing Spirits
songs.lyrics_translation: They are circling around in the sky (preparatory to going away)

songs.title: Healing Song from the Spirit Women (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am going into mud turtle's house

songs.title: Healing Song from the Spirit Women (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: The east women help me all night

songs.title: I Use My Medicine to Cure the Sick
songs.lyrics_translation: I use my medicine to cure her

songs.title: I Give You Medicine to Drink
comments: Densmore notates this without meter or barlines, adding there are "No perceptible accents". Also, she writes "Two renditions of the songs were recorded and are uniform in every respect"
songs.lyrics_translation: I will at least try to give you this medicine to drink

songs.title: I Will Drive the Sickness Out of You
I Am Rewarding You
songs.lyrics_translation: The power above said, It is I who am now rewarding you so that you will live to old age

songs.title: The Heavens Help You
songs.lyrics_translation: The heavens speak and help you and others will depend upon you for help

songs.title: Healing Song (b)
comments: Densmore gives the drum tempo as quaver=184bpm

songs.title: Two Sides of the Heavens
songs.lyrics_translation: The two sides of the heavens are coming together

songs.title: Funeral Song (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: A path on which he goes

songs.title: Manabus and the Stone (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am going inside

songs.title: Manabus and the Stone (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: I am going into the green-clouds wigwam

songs.title: Manabus Challenges the Underwater Snake
songs.lyrics_translation: Come and swallow me

songs.title: I Will Hide My Bullet
songs.lyrics_translation: I will hide my bullet in the ground so no one can find it

songs.lyrics_translation: I will beat you anyway. You are not smart enough

songs.title: Love Song (b)
songs.lyrics_translation: You had better go home, your mother loves you so much

file.rawMarkdownBody:
Downloading
-----------

This dataset is part of the *Densmore Collection*, which can be downloaded from Daniel Shanahan's [GitHub repository](https://github.com/shanahdt/densmore/). 
All files in this subset are in the [`Densmore/menominee`](https://github.com/shanahdt/densmore/tree/master/Densmore/menominee) directory.

Catafolk notes
--------------

- Densmore reports the songs were collected in Keshena, Neopit and Zoar, all of which lie \
Menominee County, Wisconsin. All songs are assigned that location.


Notes on additional metadata
----------------------------

Additional metadata can be found in this
[Google Docs sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fWUdnKA8xeRsh2tUteiYDEqjwVY5S6LOlyLwRVaq7lA)

- If there was no indication of the use of a drum (e.g. a drum tempo, or a drum trancription),
    the song is assumed to be monophonic.
- Meters were transcribed (mostly) in order of occurance (but every meter is included only once)
- Tempo transcriptions generally follow the tempo indication for the voice (sometimes a drum tempo is also indicated)
